flowchart TD
    A[example run\nsituation.md plus linked files] --> B[sign.sh\nregenerate keypair,\npublic key, signature]
    B --> C[adc complain\ndraft complaint.md]
    C --> D[adc case]

    D --> E[stage complaint files\nand generate case packet]
    E --> F[generate plaintiff strategy\nand defense strategy]
    F --> G[build scenario with case_init\nand no case-specific turns]
    G --> H[Lean initialize_case\nseed complaint and attachments]
    H --> I[next_opportunity loop]
    I --> J[log agent call\nrole, phase, reason,\nallowed tools]
    J --> K{delegated role?}
    K -- no --> L[local model call]
    K -- yes --> M[ACP agent session\npi-acp and pi in Podman\nwith ephemeral home only]
    L --> N[decision or pass]
    M --> N
    N --> O[Lean apply_decision\nvalidate opportunity]
    O --> P{accepted?}
    P -- no --> Q[plain-language correction\nsame opportunity]
    Q --> N
    P -- yes --> R[execute accepted act\nLean step or runner action]
    R --> S[update state,\nsqlite run db,\nand events]
    S --> T{terminal?}
    T -- no --> I
    T -- yes --> U[write run.json,\ntranscript.md,\ndigest.md]
